<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0;" name="viewport" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>分享有礼</title>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://res.wx.qq.com/open/js/jweixin-1.3.2.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/fleiable.js"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px;
        }
        .bg {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
        }
        .first, .second, .third {
            position: relative;
        }
        .btn-share {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 1rem;
            z-index: 99;
            left: 50%;
            margin-left: -2.5rem;
        }
        .btn-text {
            font-size: 0.35rem;
            color: #fff;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            margin-top: -0.5rem;
            left: 50%;
            margin-left: -1.1rem;
        }
        .btn-share img {
            width: 5rem;
        }
        .rule-content {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0px;
            font-size: 0.31rem;
            color: #36383A;
            padding: 1.2rem; 
            top: 1.2rem;
        }
        .rule-content .rule {
            line-height: .6rem;
            margin-top: .1rem;
        }
        .get-info-con {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0px;
            left: 0px;
            padding: 0 1.3rem; 
            padding-top: .6rem;
            font-size: 0.35rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            align-items: center;
            width: calc(100% - 2.6rem);
            height: 100%;
        }
        .get-info-con .item {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .get-info-con .item .show {
            font-size: .6rem;
        }
        .get-info-con .item .title {
            font-size: .35rem;
            color: #919191;
            margin-top: .2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="first">
        <img class="bg" src="./img/img_bg_share_one.png">
        <div class="btn-share">
            <img src="./img/icon_share_button.png">
            <span class="btn-text">邀请好友赚10元</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="second">
        <img src="./img/img_bg_accumulation_of_gifts.png"  class="bg">
        <div class="get-info-con">
           <div class="item">
               <div class="show">10元</div>
               <div class="title">红包在路上</div>
           </div>
           <div class="item">
                <div class="show">10元</div>
                <div class="title">累计获得</div>
           </div>
           <div class="item">
                <div class="show">2人</div>
                <div class="title">成功邀请</div>
           </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="third">
        <img src="./img/img_detailed_rules_of_the_activities.png" class="bg">
        <div class="rule-content">
            <div class="rule">1.活动时间：2018年08月01日-2018年08月31日24点</div>
            <div class="rule">2.好友领取您送出的红包，并在活动时间内完成买券，无论是否使用领取的红包，您均可获得10元红包奖励</div>
            <div class="rule">3.红包会在邀请成功后48小时内发放入您的账号，您可在超盟U品小程序中查看</div>
            <div class="rule">4.你能邀请的好友必须是超盟U品的新用户，同一手机号同一微信号视为同一用户</div>
            <div class="rule">5.如有其他疑问请咨询超盟U品客服</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>